Global setup:

 Download and install Git
  git config --global user.name "Your Name"
  git config --global user.email dhydrated@gmail.com
        

Next steps:

  mkdir hector-examples
  cd hector-examples
  git init
  touch README
  git add README
  git commit -m 'first commit'
  git remote add origin git@github.com:dhydrated/hector-examples.git OR https://dhydrated@github.com/dhydrated/hector-examples.git
  git push -u origin master
      

Existing Git Repo?

  cd existing_git_repo
  git remote add origin git@github.com:dhydrated/hector-examples.git OR https://dhydrated@github.com/dhydrated/hector-examples.git
  git push -u origin master
      
